MY KHChKM VMY YVD'y PhShUr DBUr ChKMTh 'aDM Th'aYUr PhNYV V'yZ PhNYV YShN'a.
'aNY PhY-MLK ShMVUr V'yL DBUrTh ShBV'yTh 'aLHYM.
'aL-ThBHL MPhNYV ThLK 'aL-Th'yMD BDBUr Ur'y KY KL-'aShUr YChPhTSh Y'yShH.
B'aShUr DBUr-MLK ShLTVN VMY Y'aMUr-LV MH-Th'yShH.
ShVMUr MTShVH L'a YD'y DBUr Ur'y V'yTh VMShPhT YD'y LB ChKM.
KY LKL-ChPhTSh YSh 'yTh VMShPhT KY-Ur'yTh H'aDM UrBH 'yLYV.
KY-'aYNNV YD'y MH-ShYHYH KY K'aShUr YHYH MY YGYD LV.
'aYN 'aDM ShLYT BUrVCh LKLV'a 'aTh-HUrVCh V'aYN ShLTVN BYVM HMVTh V'aYN MShLChTh BMLChMH VL'a-YMLT UrSh'y 'aTh-B'yLYV.
'aTh-KL-ZH Ur'aYThY VNThVN 'aTh-LBY LKL-M'yShH 'aShUr N'yShH ThChTh HShMSh 'yTh 'aShUr ShLT H'aDM B'aDM LUr'y LV.
VBKN Ur'aYThY UrSh'yYM QBUrYM VB'aV VMMQVM QDVSh YHLKV VYShThKChV B'yYUr 'aShUr KN-'yShV GM-ZH HBL.
'aShUr 'aYN-N'yShH PhThGM M'yShH HUr'yH MHUrH 'yL-KN ML'a LB BNY-H'aDM BHM L'yShVTh Ur'y.
'aShUr ChT'a 'yShH Ur'y M'aTh VM'aUrYK LV KY GM-YVD'y 'aNY 'aShUr YHYH-TVB LYUr'aY H'aLHYM 'aShUr YYUr'aV MLPhNYV.
VTVB L'a-YHYH LUrSh'y VL'a-Y'aUrYK YMYM KTShL 'aShUr 'aYNNV YUr'a MLPhNY 'aLHYM.
YSh-HBL 'aShUr N'yShH 'yL-H'aUrTSh 'aShUr YSh TShDYQYM 'aShUr MGY'y 'aLHM KM'yShH HUrSh'yYM VYSh UrSh'yYM ShMGY'y 'aLHM KM'yShH HTShDYQYM 'aMUrThY ShGM-ZH HBL.
VShBChThY 'aNY 'aTh-HShMChH 'aShUr 'aYN-TVB L'aDM ThChTh HShMSh KY 'aM-L'aKVL VLShThVTh VLShMVCh VHV'a YLVNV B'yMLV YMY ChYYV 'aShUr-NThN-LV H'aLHYM ThChTh HShMSh.
K'aShUr NThThY 'aTh-LBY LD'yTh ChKMH VLUr'aVTh 'aTh-H'yNYN 'aShUr N'yShH 'yL-H'aUrTSh KY GM BYVM VBLYLH ShNH B'yYNYV 'aYNNV Ur'aH.
VUr'aYThY 'aTh-KL-M'yShH H'aLHYM KY L'a YVKL H'aDM LMTShV'a 'aTh-HM'yShH 'aShUr N'yShH ThChTh-HShMSh BShL 'aShUr Y'yML H'aDM LBQSh VL'a YMTSh'a VGM 'aM-Y'aMUr HChKM LD'yTh L'a YVKL LMTSh'a.
